review 1: I can confirm with the other 1 star review, came here, no one seated me. So I sat by myself, went and grab the menu, filled it, returned it back. After 40 minutes and seeing other people getting served food before me I went and ask "is my water even ready" because they didn't serve us with our beverages. They said ready ready. 5 minutes later, i went and ask again , 'ready ready'. So I just left with a hungry stomach. Never again.
review 2: Nice atmosphere, nice food and services. Prices are very affordable too.
